Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们的新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raizer  是伊恩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生让我把这机体带给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raizer对接模式  O-Raizer对接模式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对接探测！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对接上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这样又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能运作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  驱逐目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双炉机的动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们来破坏！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我们的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基宁上尉！
